This is a fork to meet my requirements. If you have no specific requirements fulfilled by this fork, 
then it would be better to use the original.

BUILDING AND INSTALLING

    Full instructions:
        See doc/html/building.html

    Quick instructions:
        ./bootstrap
        ./configure
        make
        make check
        sudo make install


For SunOS and AIX have a look at README.SunOS and README.AIX.
